  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this present study is to determine if a daily walking program of 50 continuous
      minutes (long bout) or two 25-minute bouts (short bouts) in similar volume on body weight,
      abdominal fat mass deposition and cardiometabolic measures in overweight and obese women
      receiving a low calorie diet for 24 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
